Name: Anti-Grav Bamboo-copter
About the game: The game uses the jet hole of the jet pack to control the direction of flight, and fly toward the destination. On the way, you need to evade a variety of different obstacles and traps. After reaching the finish line, accept the evaluation and unlock the next level. A total of 61 levels. Left mouse button / left arrow: Activate jet pack jet to the left.. Right mouse button / right arrow: Activate jet pack jet to the right. Shift: The aircraft accelerates forward. A: Activate the switch. Ordinary obstacles: Penalty time +0.5s after Bamboo-copter collision, body collision +5s and buckle a drop of blood. Sawtooth Obstruction: Penalty time +5s after Bamboo-copter collision, three collisions, the game is over. Body collision, the game is over. Laser: Whether the Bamboo-copter or the body collides, the game is over. Pass through condition: Arrive at the finish , the time evaluation is at least one star.
